*Fellow, Commission for Scientific Medicine and Mental Health, 2003-present<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.csmmh.org/fellows.html | title = The Commission for Scientific Medicine and Mental Health: Coordinating Committee & Fellows | accessdate = 2009-02-19 | publisher = Commission for Scientific Medicine and Mental Health }}</ref>
*Berkeley Fellow, 2005<U+2013>present
* Inclusion in The Best American Science and Nature Writing 2005, ed. Jonathan Weiner (Houghton Mifflin), 2005
* Nominated for National Book Critics Circle Award (''Follies of the Wise''), 2006

